import './App.css'; import axios from 'axios' import { useState, useEffect } from 'react' import Spinner from '../src/component/ui/Spinner' import SearchForm from '../src/component/search-form/SearchForm' function App() { const [pokemons, setPokemons] = useState([]) const [isLoading, setIsLoading] = useState(false) const getPokemon = async () => { setIsLoading(true) const result = await axios.get('http://localhost:3001/api/pokemon'); if (result.status !== 200) { setIsLoading(false) return } const list = result.data.body.results setPokemons(list) setIsLoading(false) } useEffect(() => { getPokemon(); }, []) return (

Lista de Pokemons

{ isLoading ? : <>
    { pokemons.sort((a, b) => a.name > b.name ? 1 : -1).map((pokemon, index) => { return (

  • {pokemon.name}

    • ) }) }
}
); } export default App;
